  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>To Supervise our road construction teams in coordination with the Site Supervisors.</li>\n  <li>To manage all paper works related to the construction works with keen knowledge.</li>\n  <li>To analyse and study site drawings.</li>\n  <li>To maintain the safe work procedures, risk assessment, and all safety documents as well as safety measures on-site among the team.</li>\n  <li>To set goals for performance and deadlines in ways that comply with company's plans and vision.</li>\n  <li>To motivate employees by resolving issues and making sound decisions among team.</li>\n  <li>To able to work both during day/night jobs with flexible hours, including sometimes PH/Sundays.</li>\n  <li>Available for work 24 x 7.</li>\n  <li>MUST have experience with NCE application, As-built drawings, TCP, SP Claim submission, Shoring Plan, PE design, Steel plate decking design, Gas pipe/water pipe projects, 22Kv/66Kv/230Kv/400Kv cable, Telcom projects.</li>\n  <li>MUST possess PSM, BCSS, RES, CSCPM with autocad knowledge, well versed MS Office skills.</li>\n</ul>",
